### 2. KeyWrapper (CD System)

Wraps CD system keys:

```java
class KeyWrapper implements ObjectWrapper {
  private Infokey key;

  KeyWrapper(Infokey key) {
    this.key = key;
  }

  boolean isPresent() {
    return key != null;
  }

  Object unwrap() {
    return key;
  }

  String getKeyType() {
    if (!isPresent()) return "";
    return key.getClass().getSimpleName();
  }

  // Other implementation methods
  // ...
}
```

